
GNOME3 styling update
January 31st 2013
----------------------------------------------

* Remove menu bar

* Tool title bar
   ** Forward and backward
   ** Remove view ++ --
   ** Title of the book
   ** Configuration button

 * Configuration
   ** New tab
   ** Print...
   ** Find...
   ** View
       Larger, Smaller, Normal

 * Search box always visible
    ** Only search in ALL shown books

 * When multiple tabs, expand them

 * Search within document moved to top

 * Online download
   ** List available bundles
   ** Download bundles to user directory
   ** Remove bundles
